node.text:
Summer KITCHEN AID GIVE-A-YAY CLOSED CONGRATULATIONS @zainscakesandbakes

Summer means one thing, taking some well deserved time off and getting ready for the busy holiday baking season ahead. To make sure you’re all geared up, I’ve teamed up with my favorite baking friends to bring one of you the chance to win your own new KITCHEN AID MIXER no matter where you are. 
To enter, follow my friends here:

2- L.I.K.E. And S.A.V.E. my post 
3- T.a.g. 3 baking friends. The more the higher your chances! 
4. Don’t forget to tell me the first thing you will bake if you got this mixer! 
For 10 extra entries, share on your stories! 
Open w.o.r.l.d.w.i.d.e. Starts now and ends 16 July 12 noon CST. W.i.n.n.e.r. will be announce by 18 July! Not affiliated with Facebook Inc. 
Please note I will never ask you for to click any link if you w.i.n.
